        "name": "PlayfulProcess",
        "date": "2026",
        "note": "Original grammar created from memory, synthesizing yoga asana practice, Patanjali's eight limbs, and the living traditions of Hatha, Ashtanga, Iyengar, and Yin yoga into an embodied exploration."
      }
